<h1><span id="Gunderam_Defence">Gunderam Defence</span></h1>
<h3><span id="2..._Qe7">2... Qe7</span></h3>
<p>The idea for Black is to transpose into a King's Indian Defence, but with forceful play this option is not entirely possible.
</p><p>Black could also play 3...c6,4...d6,5...Bg4 or 5...h6 and develop slowly but surely.
</p>
<p><b>1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Qe7</b>
